<h1>Andersen Silva</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://andersensilva.com/now/">andersensilva.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Lyndhurst
NJ
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
I am the Data Services Manager for Microwize Technology <<a href="http://www.microwize.com/>">http://www.microwize.com/></a> in Paramus, NJ. We are healthcare technology consultants.  I am also a singer/songwriter, as well as the rhythm guitarist for Greta's Unmentionables.  Yes, that's really our name.  ;-)
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I strive to provide a little clarity and a little levity.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I write and record songs so they don't build up inside and stretch out my skull.  I try to make the world just that much more bearable, for myself and others, because we should enjoy the ride while we're here as much as possible.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
You're almost never going to FIND the time; you need to resolve to MAKE the time.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
"Amusing Ourselves to Death: Public Discourse in the Age of Show Business" by Neil Postman
</p>

